release_note: You can now propagate profile modifications to contacts. The premium version allows you to transfer an on going voice video call from a mobile to a PC and to create multiple Spaces each with its own profile contacts conversations notifications etc. for each social group you interact with family friends business including Secret Spaces accessed by name. Pressing your profile image at the top of the screen allows you to switch the current Space by tapping its image.

You can now select and act upon multiple messages in a conversation. You can now view the media exchanged in a conversation. Contacts with the premium version can stream their music during calls launch group calls and publish QR codes from the calls tab that allow guests to call them without installing the app click to call . Pressing your profile image at the top of the screen brings a settings menu allowing you to personalize the app. When experiencing unexpected behavior zap the app in order to refresh its state. Please report problems and send feedback.

NEW: Groups are now live and they are totally secure ! Clic on Conversations Create a group. Choose a name a picture and invite your contacts to join the group. You can send text messages photos videos and encrypted documents. Group messages are as easy to use and secure as standard messages. NEW: totally secure and peer to peer groups have now arrived. SKRED the true secure messaging app offers you a unique experience through secure and confidential groups. You can now create a group by clicking on Conversations Create a group. Choose a name and a picture then invite your contacts to join the group. You can exchange messages photos videos and encrypted documents as easily as in standard messaging. The messages and files you send are not saved on a remote server they are send directly between the members of the group. This guarantees you the real confidentiality of your exhanges. Juste like with one to one messages you can also permanently delete the messages you have sent in the group. With its worldwide deployment SKRED is gradually establishing itself as the sturdy and reliable alternative to conventional messaging apps. All exchanges between users are encrypted end to end and do not go through any storage servers as it is common in traditional messaging. Encryption keys are generated locally on each device and the private key never leaves the device. This ensures that only the intended recipients can read your messages. Finally all exchanged data flows are protected by TLS Transport Layer Security protocol in order to defend any fraudulent or man in the middle attack strategy.
